        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You unleash a mighty wave from your hand that buffets back your foes. Each creature in the area must attempt a Fortitude saving throw. If a creature pushed by <em>unbreaking wave advance</em> would be pushed into a solid barrier or another creature, it stops at that point and takes 3d6 damage.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is pushed 10 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is pushed 20 feet.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage for pushing a creature into a solid barrier increases by 1d6.</p>"
